column1:
The Eternals,$20,"

You are thousands of years old. You have amazing powers. You have watched civilizations rise and fall. So why does no one remember any of this? Bestselling Author Neil Gaiman (Marvel: 1602, Anansi Boys, Sandman) is joined by superstar artist John Romita Jr. (Amazing Spider-Man, Wolverine) to present a tale that will change the Eternals and the Marvel Universe forever! Collects Eternals (2006) #1-7.

","You are thousands of years old. You have amazing powers. You have watched civilizations rise and fall",,,John,#,896-3-16-458236-0,2012,,,,,upload,,,,1,,"2019-07-23 09:45:38"

Mighty Thor,$20,"

When Dr. Jane Foster lifts the mystic hammer Mjolnir, she is transformed into the Goddess of Thunder, the Mighty Thor! Her enemies are many as Asgard descends further into chaos, and unrest threatens to spread throughout the Ten Realms. Yet she wages her greatest battle against a far more personal foe: the cancer killing her mortal form. When Loki steps back into Thor's life, will it ease her troubles or only add to her pain? There's no such question about Malekith as he continues to fan the flames of a looming War of Realms &mdash
column2:
when he isn't wedding planning, that is! And as Asgard is torn apart, the skies will shake in one of the bloodiest battles of all time: It's Thor vs. Odin like never before!

","When Dr. Jane Foster lifts the mystic hammer Mjolnir, she is transformed into the Goddess of Thunder, the Mighty Thor!",,,"Jason Aaron",#,652-3-16-789123-0,2015,,,,,upload,,,,1,,"2019-07-23 09:49:48"

column1:
C++ Programming in easy steps, 5th Edition,,"

C++ Programming in easy steps, 5th
column2: Edition
column4: how to program in the powerful C++ language. Now, in its fifth edition, this guide gives complete examples that illustrate each aspect with colourized source code.

column2: Edition
column3: begins by explaining how to install a free C++ compiler so you&nbsp
column4: can quickly begin to create your&nbsp
column5: own executable programs by copying the book&rsquo
column6: s examples. It demonstrates all the C++ language basics before moving on to provide examples of Object Oriented Programming (OOP).

column1: C++ is not platform-dependent, so programs can be created on any operating system. Most illustrations in this book depict output on the Windows operating system purely because it is the most widely used desktop platform. The examples can also be created on other platforms such as Linux or macOS.
The book concludes by demonstrating how you
column2: can use your&nbsp
column3: acquired knowledge to create programs graphically using a modern C++ Integrated Development Environment (IDE), such as Microsoft&rsquo

column2: Edition
column3: has an easy-to-follow style that will appeal to:

column1: • anyone who wants to begin programming in C++

column2: studying C++ Programming at school or college

column1: • those seeking a career in computing who need a fundamental understanding of object oriented programming
This book makes no assumption that you have
column2: previous knowledge of any programming language so it is suitable for the beginner to programming in C++, whether you&nbsp
column3:
know C or not.

","C++ Programming in easy steps, 5th Edition shows you how to program in the powerful C++ language. Now, in its fifth edition, this guide gives complete examples that illustrate each aspect with colourized source code.",,,"easy steps",,530-3-16-852364-0,2017,,,,,upload,,,,1,,"2019-07-23 11:12:31"
